      <title>以色列扫荡期间西岸汽车袭击致两名袭击者死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/two-assailants-die-in-west-bank-car-attacks-amid-israeli-sweeps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一辆汽车在约旦河西岸的一个加油站爆炸，另一辆汽车撞入附近的以色列定居点，当局称袭击者发动了恐怖袭击，两名袭击者均被击毙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/two-assailants-die-in-west-bank-car-attacks-amid-israeli-sweeps</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 00:29:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
